data.title: Group photograph, Denmark
data.meta_description: Group photograph of some of the Danish royal family, taken on steps, Left to right, standing: possibly Robert, Duc de Chartres, Francoise, Duchesse de Chartres; Princess Marie dOrleans; Prince Waldemar of Denmark; King Christian IX of Denmark; Prince George of Greece; Tsar Alexander III of Russia; King George I of the Hellenes; Albert Edward, Prince of Wales; Crown Prince Frederick of Denmark;  Princess Louise, Princess Victoria and Princess Maud of Wales; possibly Prince Henri dOrleans.
